            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <div class="card card-soft p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                        <span class="badge-soft me-2">Highlights</span>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-window-sidebar me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            Fully custom websites (no monthly builder fees)
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-code-slash me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            Complex applications with heavy logic and databases
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-hdd-network me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            Enterprise integrations with secure, high-performance APIs
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            App migration to cloud (lift-and-shift)
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-database-check me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            Database migration with zero data loss
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line me-2 text-primary"></i>
                            Actionable dashboards & data visualization
                        </li>
                    </ul>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Three ways we make your life easier</h2>
        <p class="lead-muted mb-4">We handle the tech stuff so you can focus on running your business.</p>
        <div class="row g-4">

            <!-- 1. Peace of Mind -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card card-soft p-4 h-100">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2 text-primary"></i>
                        Peace of Mind
                    </h5>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        Tell us what you need, then relax. We take care of everything—from setup to launch—so you never have to stress about the tech side.
                    </p>
                    <a asp-action="Services" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost">See how we help</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. Quality You Can Trust -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card card-soft p-4 h-100">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">
                        <i class="bi bi-award me-2 text-primary"></i>
                        Quality You Can Trust
                    </h5>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        20+ years of building software means we know how to make your site and app look amazing, work smoothly, and impress your customers.
                    </p>
                    <a asp-action="Cases" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost">Check our work</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. Real People, Real Help -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card card-soft p-4 h-100">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">
                        <i class="bi bi-people me-2 text-primary"></i>
                        Real People, Real Help
                    </h5>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        No bots here. Just real humans who answer your questions, give honest advice, and offer free expert consultations.
                    </p>
                    <a asp-action="Pricing" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost">Let’s chat</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

