    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What Small Business Customers Really Care About</h2>
        <p class="lead-muted mb-4">We’ve done our homework, so we focus on the things that matter most to you.</p>

        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li class="mb-3">
                <strong>✅ Credibility that wins trust:</strong> Your site should make you look professional from the first click. We design websites that reflect your brand and build instant trust.
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <strong>✅ Simple and mobile-friendly:</strong> Most of your visitors are on their phones—so we make sure your site works beautifully on any device.
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <strong>✅ Clear calls to action:</strong> A great website isn’t just pretty—it guides visitors to contact you, book a service, or buy from you without confusion.
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <strong>✅ Peace of mind:</strong> You’ve got enough on your plate. We handle the tech so you can focus on running your business, stress-free.
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <strong>✅ Reliable results:</strong> We build websites that load fast, stay secure, and help turn visitors into paying customers.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>



